These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  fisherman, accountant, chef, firefighter, writer, software-developer, manager
There are 7 different nationalities: egyptian, colombian, dutch, malaysian, spanish, russian, polish
 1. the firefighter is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the spanish is the firefighter##1
 3. the manager is on the right of the software-developer##1
 4. the dutch is on the right of the russian##1
 5. the chef is in the middle##1
 6. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 7. the writer is the egyptian##1
 8. the fisherman is on the right of the russian##1
 9. the dutch is on the left of the colombian##1
10. the malaysian is on the left of the chef##1
11. the manager is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | writer | firefighter | accountant | chef | fisherman | software-developer | manager |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | spanish   | malaysian      | russian | dutch    | colombian    | polish         |

