.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pumpkin, artichoke, spinach, asparagus, corn, tomato, papaya
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: house, indie, trance, ambient, disco, jazz, classical
 1. the fan of disco is the person eating asparagus##1
 2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 5. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 7. the fan of disco is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
10. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | pumpkin | artichoke | corn | asparagus | tomato | papaya | spinach |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | trance   | ambient   | disco      | house       | classical       | jazz     |

