.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, tomato, broccoli, cherry, pineapple, kale, kiwi
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, firefighter, social-worker, security-guard, architect, accountant, paramedic
 1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the paramedic##1
 3. the firefighter is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 4. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 5. the librarian is the person eating pineapple##1
 6. the social-worker is on the right of the firefighter##1
 7. the firefighter is on the left of the social-worker##1
 8. the firefighter is on the right of the security-guard##1
 9. the person eating kale is the security-guard##1
10. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the librarian##1
11. the security-guard is in the middle##1
12. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | tomato | pineapple     | broccoli  | kale       | cranberry       | kiwi  | cherry   |
| Job    | accountant  | librarian | paramedic | security-guard | firefighter | social-worker | architect |

