.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, blues, techno, d&b, reggae, soul, house
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, canadian, spanish, british, dutch, italian, german
 1. the fan of reggae is the canadian##1
 2. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 3. the italian is on the right of the spanish##1
 4. the russian is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 5. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 6. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
 7. the spanish is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 8. the fan of techno is on the right of the italian##1
 9. the fan of techno is the dutch##1
10. the dutch is on the left of the fan of blues##1
11. the german is the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | house     | d&b     | techno      | blues | reggae      | classical     |
| Nationality   | british | spanish | italian | dutch | german | canadian | russian |

