.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, hiking, photography, rock-climbing, singing, dancing, skydiving
7 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, goat, chinchilla, ferret, cat, rabbit
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | hiking | photography | dancing     | rock-climbing | skydiving | singing | woodworking |
| Pet     | rabbit   | goat    | ferret | cat     | hamster         | chinchilla     | lizard        |

