.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, milk, lemonade, tea
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, train, motorbike, snowmobile, van, airplane, helicopter
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the boat##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | lemonade   | fanta | mirinda | tea  | milk | cola |
| Transport   | snowmobile   | van | boat | airplane     | train | helicopter | motorbike   |

