.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, romance, family, musical, fantasy, disaster, sports
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, scooter, airplane, bike, tram, quad-bike, van
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the person driving the car is the person watching family movies##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | sports | musical | fantasy | disaster     | romance | family |
| Transport     | quad-bike | bike      | van | airplane    | tram | scooter   | car  |

