 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | drawing   | hiking | traveling | card-games | dancing | sudoku  |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | spy | satire  | horror | adventure | fantasy     | action |

